dc_description_s: This data represents boundaries of Wisconsin Department of Workforce Development's Workforce Development Areas, Wisconsin in 2021. [Since each WDA region is comprised of one or more counties, this feature layer was built from Wisconsin DNR's county feature layer. The county data is derived from 1:24,000-scale sources. The county feature class was last updated in June 2015; refer to the Data Lineage section of the ArcGIS metadata for information about the nature of the update. For more information, contact the WI DNR Bureau of Technology Services.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-wi-dpi.opendata.arcgis.com/
